        {
            "id": "tradingview:b244da4be10f6:0",
            "title": "PetMed Express To Sell Delray Beach Headquarters For $37 Million In Sale-Leaseback With Redfearn",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>PetMed Express entered into a real estate sale-leaseback with Redfearn Capital Acquisitions to sell its properties at 410 and 420 South Congress Avenue, Delray Beach, for $37.0 million and lease back its 100,519-square-foot headquarters. The buyer will place $0.5 million and $1.7 million in escrow around the due diligence period, which can extend up to 45 days, with closing 30 days after diligence ends. The 10-year triple-net lease starts at $15.25 per square foot with 3.5% annual increases, includes three 5-year extension options at market rent with 3.5% annual bumps, requires prepayment of the third year’s base rent, and a security deposit equal to one year’s rent. The deal is intended to monetize real estate and enhance liquidity.</span></p><p class=\"\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Agreement details:</span></strong></p><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Agreement type</span></strong><span>: Real estate sale-leaseback of headquarters and adjacent property</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Counterparty</span></strong><span>: Redfearn Capital Acquisitions</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Signed / Effective</span></strong><span>: Jul 23 2026 / Jul 23 2026</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Duration / Termination</span></strong><span>: 10-year initial lease term with three 5-year extension options</span></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><strong class=\"root-Tkn6WL2y\"><span>Reason</span></strong><span>: Unlock real estate value and fund operations</span></li></ul><p class=\"\"><span>Original SEC Filing: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec icon-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1040130/000104013026000029/pets-20260723.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">PETMED EXPRESS INC [ PETS ] - 8-K - Jul. 23, 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-powered summary. It may contain inaccuracies. Consider verifying important information with the source. Please note this summary is solely based on documents filed with the SEC.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
